---
title: Quick Peri Peri Chicken & Cheese Sandwich with Salt & Vinegar Fries
description: The craving for a good sandwich has been here for a while now, but the wait is over! Sink your teeth into a Parmesan
crumbed chicken sandwich, slathered in a mayo on the base and fresh salad extras on the top. Enjoy it with a side of fries drizzled in the right amount of vinegar to fit your tastes.
